Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chính là cậu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Đại ca, đại ca, đại ca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Đại ca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Đại ca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Là cậu à, quan gia.
