Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,ta đẩy ở phía sau cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Được thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nào, đi.
